    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<center>本文主要用于记录，对 hexo 博客部署平台的介绍以及使用。</center> <span id="more"></span><h1 id="hexo-dui-hexo-kai-fa-ge-ren-bo-ke-de-jie-shao-yi-huan-jing-bu-shu-pei-zhi">【hexo】对 hexo 开发个人博客的介绍（一）— 环境部署配置</h1><p>本文主要用于记录，并使用 hexo 进行开发个人博客，并将博客部署到 github page 和 vercel 关联部署站点。</p><h2 id="ji-ben-huan-jing-pei-zhi" id="基本环境配置">基本环境配置</h2><ol><li>git 工具</li><li>npm 工具</li><li>node.js</li></ol><h3 id="cha-kan-huan-jing-pei-zhi" id="查看环境配置">查看环境配置</h3><p>在终端输入以下代码可以查看工具在电脑环境中的安装情况</p><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">node</span> <span class="title">-v</span></span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line">git --<span class="keyword">version</span></span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#如下</span></span><br><span class="line">cs@bogon Desktop % <span class="keyword">node</span> <span class="title">-v</span></span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line">git --<span class="keyword">version</span></span><br><span class="line">v16.<span class="number">16.0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">8.11</span>.<span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="keyword">version</span> <span class="number">2.32</span>.<span class="number">1</span> (Apple Git-<span class="number">133</span>)</span><br><span class="line">cs@bogon Desktop %</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="an-zhuang-git-gong-ju" id="安装-git-工具">安装 git 工具</h3><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/liuzehn/article/details/124313436">《三种常见的 Mac 安装 git 工具的方法》</a> 进行 git 工具的安装。</p><h3 id="an-zhuang-node-js" id="安装-node-js">安装 node.js</h3><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/w956443578w/article/details/124073146">《Mac 安装 node.js 及环境配置》</a> 进行 node.js 工具的安装。</p><h3 id="an-zhuang-npm-gong-ju" id="安装-npm-工具">安装 npm 工具</h3><p>node.js 自带 npm 工具。</p><h2 id="bo-ke-bu-shu-gong-ju" id="博客部署工具">博客部署工具</h2><h3 id="an-zhuang-hexo-bo-ke-gong-ju" id="安装-hexo-博客工具">安装 hexo 博客工具</h3><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/wapchief/article/details/54602515">《使用 hexo+github 免费搭建个人博客网站超详细教程》</a> 进行 hexo 的安装以及配置 github page 部署站点的基本信息。</p><h3 id="tian-jia-xin-cai-dan-fen-lei-ye-mian" id="添加新菜单分类页面">添加新菜单分类页面</h3><p>参考此博客 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/wangqingchuan92/article/details/111933517">【个人网站搭建】GitHub pages+hexo 框架下为 next 主题添加菜单分类页面</a></p><h4 id="1-shi-yong-zhi-ling-tian-jia-ye-mian" id="1-使用指令添加页面">1. 使用指令添加页面</h4><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cs@bogon blog_hexo_github % hexo new page <span class="string">&quot;share&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  ==================================</span><br><span class="line">  ███╗   ██╗███████╗██╗  ██╗████████╗</span><br><span class="line">  ████╗  ██║██╔════╝╚██╗██╔╝╚══██╔══╝</span><br><span class="line">  ██╔██╗ ██║█████╗   ╚███╔╝    ██║</span><br><span class="line">  ██║╚██╗██║██╔══╝   ██╔██╗    ██║</span><br><span class="line">  ██║ ╚████║███████╗██╔╝ ██╗   ██║</span><br><span class="line">  ╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝   ╚═╝</span><br><span class="line">========================================</span><br><span class="line">NexT version <span class="number">8.12</span>.<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">Documentation: https:<span class="regexp">//</span>theme-<span class="keyword">next</span>.js.org</span><br><span class="line">========================================</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: ~<span class="regexp">/Downloads/</span>cs_workspace<span class="regexp">/cs_home_page/</span>cs_hexo_blog<span class="regexp">/SVN_MAC_LOCAL/</span>blog_hexo_github<span class="regexp">/source/</span>share/index.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-xiu-gai-zhu-ti-she-zhi-yml-wen-jian" id="2-修改主题设置-yml-文件">2. 修改主题设置 yml 文件</h4><p>打开主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，定位到 <code>menu</code>，添加如下内容：</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  share:</span> /share || fa fa-heartbeat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-jiang-xin-tian-jia-de-fen-lei-ye-mian-ming-cheng-xian-shi-cheng-zhong-wen" id="3-将新添加的分类页面名称显示成中文">3. 将新添加的分类页面名称显示成中文</h4><p>打开 <code>hexo-&gt;theme-&gt;next-&gt;languages-&gt;zh-Hans.yml</code>，在 <code>menu</code> 下添加：</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  home:</span> 首页</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  archives:</span> 归档</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  categories:</span> 分类</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  tags:</span> 标签</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  about:</span> 关于</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  search:</span> 搜索</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  schedule:</span> 日程表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  sitemap:</span> 站点地图</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  commonweal:</span> 公益<span class="number">404</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  share:</span> 咨询分享</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="" id=""></h2><h1 id="hexo-dui-hexo-kai-fa-ge-ren-bo-ke-de-jie-shao-er-yang-shi-pei-zhi">【hexo】对 hexo 开发个人博客的介绍（二）— 样式配置</h1><p>本文主要用于记录，通过对主题配置文件和站点配置文件的配置以及额外工具包的安装。</p><h1 id="can-kao-yang-shi-pei-zhi">参考样式配置</h1><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.panoshu.top/blog/fbbe79ce/">《Hexo 博客免费部署方案以及 Vercel 托管并使用 CND 加速访问》</a></p><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.panoshu.top/blog/cb27ab6f/">《Hexo 博客 NexT 主题设置之使用 HarmonyOS 字体》</a></p><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.panoshu.top/blog/9db7e29f/">《Hexo 博客 NexT 主题设置之 KaTex 公式与 Markdown 复杂表格》</a></p><h1 id="hexo-dui-hexo-kai-fa-ge-ren-bo-ke-de-jie-shao-san-pei-zhi-xiao-cao-zuo">【hexo】对 hexo 开发个人博客的介绍（三）— 配置小操作</h1><p>本文主要用于记录，并使用 hexo 进行开发个人博客的常用指令和配置</p><h2 id="tian-jia-xin-cai-dan-fen-lei-ye-mian-1" id="添加新菜单分类页面-2">添加新菜单分类页面</h2><p>参考此博客 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/wangqingchuan92/article/details/111933517">【个人网站搭建】GitHub pages+hexo 框架下为 next 主题添加菜单分类页面</a></p><h3 id="1-shi-yong-zhi-ling-tian-jia-ye-mian-1" id="1-使用指令添加页面-2">1. 使用指令添加页面</h3><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cs@bogon blog_hexo_github % hexo new page <span class="string">&quot;share&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  ==================================</span><br><span class="line">  ███╗   ██╗███████╗██╗  ██╗████████╗</span><br><span class="line">  ████╗  ██║██╔════╝╚██╗██╔╝╚══██╔══╝</span><br><span class="line">  ██╔██╗ ██║█████╗   ╚███╔╝    ██║</span><br><span class="line">  ██║╚██╗██║██╔══╝   ██╔██╗    ██║</span><br><span class="line">  ██║ ╚████║███████╗██╔╝ ██╗   ██║</span><br><span class="line">  ╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝   ╚═╝</span><br><span class="line">========================================</span><br><span class="line">NexT version <span class="number">8.12</span>.<span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">Documentation: https:<span class="regexp">//</span>theme-<span class="keyword">next</span>.js.org</span><br><span class="line">========================================</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Created: ~<span class="regexp">/Downloads/</span>cs_workspace<span class="regexp">/cs_home_page/</span>cs_hexo_blog<span class="regexp">/SVN_MAC_LOCAL/</span>blog_hexo_github<span class="regexp">/source/</span>share/index.md</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-xiu-gai-zhu-ti-she-zhi-yml-wen-jian-1" id="2-修改主题设置-yml-文件-2">2. 修改主题设置 yml 文件</h3><p>打开主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，定位到 <code>menu</code>，添加如下内容：</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  share:</span> /share || fa fa-heartbeat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-jiang-xin-tian-jia-de-fen-lei-ye-mian-ming-cheng-xian-shi-cheng-zhong-wen-1" id="3-将新添加的分类页面名称显示成中文-2">3. 将新添加的分类页面名称显示成中文</h3><p>打开 <code>hexo-&gt;theme-&gt;next-&gt;languages-&gt;zh-Hans.yml</code>，在 <code>menu</code> 下添加：</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  home:</span> 首页</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  archives:</span> 归档</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  categories:</span> 分类</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  tags:</span> 标签</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  about:</span> 关于</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  search:</span> 搜索</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  schedule:</span> 日程表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  sitemap:</span> 站点地图</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  commonweal:</span> 公益<span class="number">404</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  share:</span> 咨询分享</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="tian-jia-ping-lun-mian-ban" id="添加评论面板">添加评论面板</h2><ul><li>参考 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_48927364/article/details/123321038">nexT 主题使用攻略基础 —— 添加评论功能</a></li><li>参考 <a href="https://waline.js.org/guide/get-started.html">waline 评论系统开始指南</a></li><li>参考 <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/535607671">hexo 添加 waline 评论系统</a></li><li>参考 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/xingyuzhongxuan/article/details/125404906">腾讯云 cloudbase 搭建 waline 评论系统</a></li></ul><h3 id="1-qian-hou-duan-pei-zhi" id="1-前后端配置">1. 前后端配置</h3><p>使用 waline 评论系统。根据指南进行评论系统前后端的配置。</p><h3 id="2-an-zhuang-hexo-waline-zu-jian" id="2-安装-hexo-waline-组件">2. 安装 hexo waline 组件</h3><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install <span class="symbol">@waline</span>/hexo-<span class="keyword">next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-pei-zhi-zhu-ti-pei-zhi-yml-wen-jian" id="3-配置主题配置-yml-文件">3. 配置主题配置 yml 文件</h3><p>打开主题配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>，添加如下内容：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">waline:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment">#是否开启</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">serverURL:</span> <span class="string">https://%%%%%%%%%%.vercel.app</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Waline #服务端地址，我们这里就是上面部署的 Vercel 地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">locale:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">placeholder:</span> <span class="string">疑义相与析，畅所欲言，不登录也没关系哒</span> <span class="comment"># #评论框的默认文字</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">mm</span> <span class="comment"># 头像风格</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">meta:</span> [<span class="string">nick</span>,<span class="string">mail</span>] <span class="comment"># 自定义评论框上面的三个输入框的内容</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">pageSize:</span> <span class="number">10</span> <span class="comment"># 评论数量多少时显示分页</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">lang:</span> <span class="string">zh-cn</span> <span class="comment"># 语言, 可选值: en, zh-cn</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">visitor:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 文章阅读统计</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">comment_count:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 如果为 false , 评论数量只会在当前评论页面显示, 主页则不显示</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">requiredFields:</span> [<span class="string">nick</span>] <span class="comment"># 设置用户评论时必填的信息，[nick,mail]: [nick] | [nick, mail]</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">libUrl:</span> <span class="comment"># Set custom library cdn url</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">login:</span> <span class="string">enable</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最终方案 选择（ Leanclound 作为评论数据库，在 Vercel 上部署服务端）该方案太慢了，可能使用自建服务器，或者买一些云服务来使用的好。</p><h2 id="wen-zhang-zhi-ding" id="文章置顶">文章置顶</h2><ul><li>参考 <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/701a7ca9ba2d">小红书关于 hexo 的操作</a></li></ul><h3 id="1-an-zhuang-zhi-ding-cha-jian" id="1-安装置顶插件">1. 安装置顶插件</h3><figure class="highlight fortran"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm uninstall hexo-generator-<span class="built_in">index</span> --<span class="keyword">save</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-<span class="built_in">index</span>-pin-top --<span class="keyword">save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-pei-zhi-wen-zhang-tou-bu" id="2-配置文章头部">2. 配置文章头部</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">文章名称</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2021-09-01 09:36:05</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span> [<span class="string">标签1</span>,<span class="string">标签2</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">&quot;类别&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">comments:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 是否可评论</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 是否显示文章目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">top:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># 置顶设置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="kan-ban-mao" id="看板猫">看板猫</h2><ul><li><p>参考 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_48927364/article/details/123321038">nexT 主题使用攻略基础 —— 添加评论功能</a></p></li><li><p>参考 <a href="https://waline.js.org/guide/get-started.html">waline 评论系统开始指南</a></p></li><li><p>参考 <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/535607671">hexo 添加 waline 评论系统</a></p></li><li><p>参考 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/xingyuzhongxuan/article/details/125404906">腾讯云 cloudbase 搭建 waline 评论系统</a></p></li><li><p>参考 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44517301/article/details/106348887">Hexo 添加 Live2D 看板娘最新教程</a></p></li><li><p>参考 <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/701a7ca9ba2d">小红书关于 hexo 的操作</a></p></li><li><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.panoshu.top/blog/fbbe79ce/">《Hexo 博客免费部署方案以及 Vercel 托管并使用 CND 加速访问》</a></p></li><li><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.panoshu.top/blog/cb27ab6f/">《Hexo 博客 NexT 主题设置之使用 HarmonyOS 字体》</a></p></li><li><p>查看此博客文档: <a href="https://blog.panoshu.top/blog/9db7e29f/">《Hexo 博客 NexT 主题设置之 KaTex 公式与 Markdown 复杂表格》</a></p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
